job_description:
GENERAL STATEMENT OF DUTIES: Performs a variety of semi-skilled park maintenance tasks which require manipulative skills; operates a variety of light equipment and machinery including but not limited to trucks, tractors, and mowers; works under the supervision of a higher classified employee and may be required to provide direction to seasonal employees; performs related duties as required.
STATEMENT OF TASKS:
Performs grounds maintenance including mowing, raking, seeding, watering,
trimming, planting and fertilizing;
Gathers refuse and rubbish from park areas;
Assists in making minor repairs to buildings and equipment;
Performs routine custodial work in park buildings and equipment;
Performs semi-skilled duties in the construction and repair of park projects.
